ModuleContextControl

Interaction logic for ModuleContextControl.xaml The ModuleContextControl is a horizontal / slim control that displays a context path to the currently displayed module. Interaction is allowed to select different modules along the path and provide feedback for the user to see which set of modules the active module exists under.
